description_with_entities.text: This group on Facebook will help FSU Seminole fans in Western North Carolina connect and plan events.  Please invite other FSU fans and alumni to join this group. The group is set up as a closed group to prevent spam. However, we definitely want all Seminole fans in the area to join. If you join, you will be approved as soon as possible.
